---
import PageLayout from '../../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="The Right Functionality to Manage US Dollar Invoices | Case Study"
  description="How Zygo used HedgeFlows to reduce currency risks from price increases in containers due to Covid."
>
  <section class="section-padding">
    <div class="container-content max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Breadcrumb -->
      <nav class="mb-8 text-[0.875rem] text-text-muted">
        <a href="/case-studies" class="hover:text-brand-green transition-colors">Case Studies</a>
        <span class="mx-2">/</span>
        <span class="text-text-heading font-medium">Zygo</span>
      </nav>

      <!-- Tags -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-brand-green-pale text-brand-green text-[0.8125rem] font-semibold rounded-full">
          Logistics
        </span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-text-muted text-[0.8125rem] font-medium rounded-full">
          Risk Management
        </span>
        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-text-muted text-[0.8125rem] font-medium rounded-full">
          Digitalisation
        </span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-[2rem] md:text-[2.5rem] font-bold text-text-heading leading-tight mb-4">
        The right functionality to manage US Dollar invoices effectively
      </h1>
      <p class="text-[1.25rem] text-brand-green font-semibold mb-10">Zygo</p>

      <!-- Pull Quote -->
      <blockquote class="my-10 p-8 bg-brand-green-pale rounded-xl border-l-4 border-brand-green">
        <p class="text-[1.125rem] text-text-heading leading-relaxed italic">
          &ldquo;HedgeFlows gave us the autonomy and the visibility into the moving market to understand our exposure and risk. We wanted to take more control and be able to manage US Dollar invoices better, and the HedgeFlows platform has helped us do this easily.&rdquo;
        </p>
        <cite class="block mt-4 text-[0.9375rem] text-text-body not-italic font-medium">
          &mdash; Charlotte, Operations Manager
        </cite>
      </blockquote>

      <!-- Content Sections -->
      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider">THE COMPANY</span>
        <h2 class="text-[1.375rem] font-bold text-text-heading mt-1 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-7 bg-brand-green rounded-full inline-block"></span>
          Freight forwarding and logistics services
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-body">
          <p>Zygo has provided Freight Forwarding and Logistics Services since the nineties. They've got expertise in a number of areas including logistics, statutory compliance, risk management and finance and payment.</p>
<p>Brexit and Covid have had an impact on how much they pay for their containers in recent years. The team at Zygo is relying on their expertise and technology to navigate these changes and manage their foreign payment processes in a more cost-effective way.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider">THE PROBLEM</span>
        <h2 class="text-[1.375rem] font-bold text-text-heading mt-1 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-7 bg-brand-green rounded-full inline-block"></span>
          Navigating high prices after Covid
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-body">
          <p>After Covid, container prices increased exponentially. With these price rises, Zygo's exposure also increased. The team felt they needed a solution to get a handle of the situation when buying their US Dollars.</p>
<p>Previously, they would work with companies and get quotes for specific figures they needed to make a payment for. They didn't have a platform that gave them the autonomy and the visibility into the moving market and their exposure.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider">THE SOLUTION</span>
        <h2 class="text-[1.375rem] font-bold text-text-heading mt-1 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-7 bg-brand-green rounded-full inline-block"></span>
          The right visibility to manage risk
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-body">
          <p>HedgeFlows gave Zygo the autonomy and visibility into the moving market to understand their exposure and risk. The platform allowed them to take more control and manage US Dollar invoices better.</p>
<p>For Charlotte at Zygo, using a platform that integrates with their accounting system (Sage) has completely changed how they manage foreign invoices. Rather than having to manually put invoices in a spreadsheet, the automatic connection into Sage saves the team significant time.</p>
        </div>
        <figure class="mt-6">
          <img src="https://8698300.hs-sites.com/hs-fs/hubfs/Laptop%20HedgeFlows_t%20.png?width=800&name=Laptop%20HedgeFlows_t%20.png" alt="HedgeFlows currency risk management platform" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-sm" loading="lazy" />
          <figcaption class="mt-2 text-[0.8125rem] text-text-muted text-center">The HedgeFlows platform — visibility into exposure and risk</figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold text-brand-green uppercase tracking-wider">THE IMPACT</span>
        <h2 class="text-[1.375rem] font-bold text-text-heading mt-1 mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-7 bg-brand-green rounded-full inline-block"></span>
          Automating Dollar invoices to save time
        </h2>
        <div class="prose prose-body">
          <p><strong>Managing risk and exposure</strong> &mdash; With HedgeFlows you can easily see the risk and exposure based on outstanding US Dollar invoices. The platform automatically provides this information, eliminating the need to work it out manually.</p>
<p><strong>Saving time and focusing on clients</strong> &mdash; HedgeFlows frees up time for Zygo. When the US Dollars are looking after themselves, it eliminates the effort of having to upload invoices manually. HedgeFlows gives them extra time to get ahead, speak to new clients, and even take on new work.</p>
<p>According to Charlotte, the HedgeFlows offering goes beyond the platform and its functionality: the personal touch is very important. Whenever they need something, the team is there to help — and that's what makes HedgeFlows different.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <blockquote class="my-8 p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-gray-200">
        <p class="text-[1rem] text-text-body leading-relaxed italic">
          &ldquo;HedgeFlows frees up time for us. When you've got the US Dollars looking after themselves, it eliminates the effort of having to upload the invoices manually. HedgeFlows gives us extra time to get ahead and speak to new clients, and even take on new work!&rdquo;
        </p>
        <cite class="block mt-3 text-[0.875rem] text-text-muted not-italic font-medium">
          &mdash; Charlotte, Operations Manager
        </cite>
      </blockquote>

      <div class="mt-12">
        <a href="/case-studies" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-green font-semibold hover:gap-3 transition-all">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 rotate-180" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
          </svg>
          Back to case studies
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection
    headline="Want similar results for your business?"
    primaryCta={{ label: 'Book a Treasury Review', href: '/treasury-health-check' }}
  />
</PageLayout>
